[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "レスナ、聞いておくれよ！\nここのマナの結晶、どれも高純度で素晴らしい品質さ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00764",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "これだけあれば錬金術に不自由することもない！\n錬金術の復活だよ、ありがとう果ての大陸！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00765",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "はいっ！　やりましたね、ロマンさん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00766",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "早速、マナをいくつか持って帰りたいんだけど――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00767",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "んー、でもちょっと気になるんだけど。\nあそこ、建物があるでしょ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00768",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "誰か住んでるっていうか、ここ私有地なんじゃない？\nマナを持って行ったらいざこざが起こるんじゃ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00769",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "でも話をしようにも、建物の扉を叩いても\n誰も出てこなかったし、鍵もかかってたよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00770",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "あの建物はパルメ族のものだ。\nお前たちには立ち入れん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00771",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "だがマナに関しては持って行ってもらって問題ない。\n資源は好きなだけ使うがいい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00772",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "パルメ族の建物……ということは、師匠がここに？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00773",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ああ、詳しいことはザスキアやアウグストが\n説明してくれるはずだ……が",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00774",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "一向に姿を現さないようだけど？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00775",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そうなんですよね。私も先ほどからそれが\n気になっていて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00776",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "まあ、それはともかく……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00777",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "おめでとう、レスナ。\nお前は俺に並ぶ、立派な英雄となった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00778",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "英雄……ですか？\nそんなことは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00779",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "あるだろう。果ての大陸への到達だけでも偉業だが、\n頂獣ウェルテックスの撃退――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00780",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "そうね、私やユリウスでもできなかったことよ。\nあっさり親を超えてくれちゃって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00781",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "極夜の錬金党からランターナを守り、\n無数島群域との国交樹立、九偉人まで味方につけた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00782",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "他人を、しかも人間を認めるのは癪だが……\n実際、お前は大した人間だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00783",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "ああ。謙遜は美徳だけど、もっと自分をほめていい。\nみんなが集まってここにいるのはレスナの力なんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00784",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "はい……ありがとうございます！\n英雄なんて私には分不相応な称号だと思いますけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00785",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "そんなレスナちゃんだから、みんなついてきたんだよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00786",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "果ての大陸へたどり着くという目標も達成したし、\n王国の悲願も成し遂げられた……君は立派な英雄だよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00787",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……みんなの気持ち、確かに受け取りました。\n何度でも言います、ありがとう！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00788",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]